  "body_excerpt": "The algorithm used for parsing HTTP cookies in Tornado versions prior to 6.4.2 sometimes has quadratic complexity, leading to excessive CPU consumption when parsing maliciously-crafted cookie headers. This parsing occurs in the event loop thread and may block the processing of other requests.\n\nSee also CVE-2024-7592 for a similar vulnerability in cpython.",
